l the doors?"],[479,620,"I don't want anyone from the team"],[620,762,"just waltzing in here."],[762,862,"Don't worry."],[900,1054,"I locked all the doors and windows."],[1095,1212,"No one is getting in here."],[1262,1325,"Trust me."],[1362,1608,"Well, that's a little too much information."],[2050,2241,"I wasn't expecting for you to do"],[2241,2479,"all the things that you do for me, Chris."],[2687,2808,"Since we're..."],[2808,2908,"Step siblings."],[2929,3029,"I know."],[3029,3141,"But we're not blood-related."],[3175,3304,"And quite frankly,"],[3304,3500,"I could care less what the world thinks."],[3500,3600,"I care about you."],[3600,3745,"I care about how you feel."],[3775,3891,"I care about the way you look at me."],[3954,4091,"I like the way you're looking at me right now."],[4145,4279,"And how am I looking at you?"],[4337,4495,"Like you want me to kiss you."],[5329,5429,"That wasn't an accident."],[5525,5620,"It was real."]],"38":[[433,566,"Did that really just happen?"],[637,725,"It feels surreal."],[841,1129,"For the record, you kissed me first."],[1170,1287,"You were taking too long."],[1345,1500,"I got impatient."],[1850,1970,"Let me make it up to you."],[2125,2345,"That's not how apologies work."],[2483,2691,"I'm sorry, do you want a formal letter?"],[2720,2941,"Or is my mouth working just fine?"],[3829,4008,"Your mouth is working just fine."],[4179,4383,"God, Jenny, do you know what you do to me?"],[4800,4887,"Show me."],[5545,5683,"If you want me to stop, I will."],[5700,5766,"Don't stop."],[5900,6100,"I've been dreaming about this since day one."],[6625,6725,"Why'd you fight it?"],[6766,6866,"I was a coward."],[6975,7129,"I never thought that you'd want me"],[7129,7275,"the way that I want you."],[7375,7545,"Jenny, the only one I want is you."],[8066,8233,"Are you sure you locked all the windows?"],[8266,8445,"I barricaded the damn world out for you."],[8666,8762,"Just so you know,"],[8845,9100,"you are not allowed to fall in love with me."],[9166,924