house?"],[2000,2137,"We eat on that couch."],[2141,2241,"Well, you should've thought about that"],[2241,2379,"before kicking us out."],[2429,2620,"How does it feel to have all three bedrooms"],[2620,2716,"to yourself?"],[2750,2912,"I didn't ask you to leave."],[2933,3083,"I just wanted to marry you."],[3250,3437,"What is it about me that you don't like,"],[3437,3620,"that makes you go after your stepsister"],[3620,3720,"all the time?"],[3779,3958,"Well, at least I don't scheme my way"],[3958,4020,"into the rich"],[4020,4191,"like a business transaction."],[4208,4341,"Natalie, I'll tell you what."],[4400,4637,"If you really love Chris,"],[4704,4812,"why don't you tell our parents"],[4812,4975,"to let us back into the house?"],[5091,5187,"If you do,"],[5262,5670,"I'll give him to you every single Wednesday."],[5716,5800,"What?"]],"42":[[91,287,"Really? You'd do that?"],[391,475,"Why not?"],[858,1000,"Okay, it's a deal."],[1075,1208,"I get Chris every Wednesday"],[1208,1312,"as long as we're married."],[1370,1433,"And you get him"],[1433,1587,"every other day of the week."],[1587,1633,"Great."],[1737,2129,"Is Natalie maybe a little bit too desperate?"],[2129,2316,"Yeah, I think the power dynamic"],[2316,2500,"has definitely changed."],[2525,2858,"So, uh, we'll see you back at the house, Natalie."],[3029,3224,"Okay, I really hope you think of something else,"],[3224,3368,"because I'm not spending every Wednesday"],[3368,3479,"with that tramp."],[3479,3645,"Calm down, cowboy."],[3700,3900,"Nobody's going to be taking my man"],[3900,4033,"anytime soon."],[4216,4308,"Come on."],[5283,5466,"What are you two brats doing back here?"],[5708,5858,"Why are Natalie's parents doing here?"],[5954,6145,"Is this part of the plan?"],[6283,6487,"I will get Chris every Wednesday"],[6487,6720,"as long as I'm married to him."],[6720,6887,"You can have him the rest of the week."],[6908,7054,"If this recording gets out,"],[7125,7266,"I wonder how that's going to impact"],[7266,7404,"your retail business."],[7404,7591,"Mr. And Mrs. Vixen?"]],"43":[[550,695,"What the hell were you thinking, Nat?"],[745,891,"Saying those things when you're marrying"],[891,970,"into the Riggins,"],[970,1183,"the most influential family in the US?"],[1187,1433,"I was just doing what you told me to do, Dad."],[1520,1766,"To marry into the Riggins for the business deals."],[1766,1837,"Wait, wait, wait, wait."],[1841,1995,"What is this, James?"],[2025,2175,"I thought the kids loved each other,"],[2175,2358,"which is why I agreed for them to get engaged."],[2475,2670,"It was never about love for them."],[2733,2933,"Natalie was only doing what her parents"],[2933,3108,"pressured her into."],[3154,3379,"But I guess that backfired, didn't it?"],[3412,3830,"Mr. Riggins, I assure you, Natalie loves Chris."],[3908,4237,"She wouldn't have said those things so publicly."],[4350,4633,"My daughter would never stoop so low."],[4754,4991,"It must be that whore that nobody wants"],[4991,5150,"that manipulated her into this."],[5204,5516,"Well, if I am a whore that nobody wants,"],[5570,5700,"why don't I just release the tape?"],[5745,5916,"Got nothing to lose, right?"],[5987,6120,"But you know you do."],[6170,6475,"With your billion dollar business ventures,"],[6475,6695,"your IPOs, your stock prices."],[6787,7029,"Yeah, they'll all take a huge hit for sure."],[7029,7120,"Okay, no, no, no, no."],[7120,7191,"Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait."]],"44":[[30,93,"No, no, no, no, no."],[93,179,"Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait."],[179,333,"Dad, no. No."],[400,520,"Just let her release it."],[562,683,"I mean, who cares?"],[700,854,"It's obvious that I was trapped into"],[854,941,"giving that answer."],[987,1212,"Stupid, child, have I taught you nothing?"],[1275,1491,"This is gonna be bad for us either way."],[1495,1783,"We, the Vixens, build our business"],[1783,1933,"as a family brand."],[1962,2112,"Do you think our competitors are just"],[2112,2400,"gonna laugh this off, and let it go?"],[2437,2637,"I mean, you've brought shame to this family"],[2641,2804,"in the name of marriage."],[2850,3079,"All right, all of you just shut up."],[3079,3295,"I can't listen to any more bickering about family"],[3295,3425,"or business values,"],[3437,3612,"because you clearly have none."],[3612,3841,"Natalie, we're calling off this engagement."],[3841,4004,"Move back to your parents' house."],[4004,4298,"And James, our deal just became a no deal."],[4345,4637,"So take your family and fuck off right now,"],[4637,4879,"or I swear I'll make your company bankrupt."],[4920,5333,"Mr. Riggins, we are truly sorry."],[5333,5466,"Why are you still talking?"],[5466,5562,"Get the fuck out!"],[6500,6634,"You two, go to your room."],[6634,6775,"I'll figure out what to do with you later."],[7066,7125,"Come on."]],"45":[[257,513,"I miss you so much already."],[691,800,"Miss you too."],[850,1028,"I wish I could just come to your room right now."],[1445,1504,"Chris?"],[1850,1948,"Jenny."],[1979,2061,"Mom."],[2779,3037,"Stupid little bitch."],[3133,3466,"You have ruined so much for me"],[3466,3800,"and I'm not just going to sit around"],[3800,4083,"while you destroy the rest of my days"],[4083,4250,"in the Riggins house."],[4450,4550,"Goodbye."],[6283,6437,"Who are you?"],[6462,6612,"What do you want from me?"],[6658,6879,"Your mother seems to be a generous woman."],[6958,7208,"She sold you to me for a generous price"],[7225,7666,"and told me I could do whatever I want with you."],[7679,7754,"No!"],[7850,7958,"No, somebody, help."],[7958,8037,"Please!"],[8091,8170,"Help!"]],"46":[[125,179,"Jenny!"],[270,416,"Hey, Jen- Jenny!"],[650,704,"Jenny!"],[1391,1458,"It's dead."],[1662,1879,"Jenny always charges her phone before bed though."],[2354,2479,"Dad, where the hell is Jenny?"],[2537,2666,"Good morning to you too, son."],[2816,2862,"I don't know,"],[2862,3016,"I haven't decided what to do with you two yet."],[3037,3150,"Okay, I can't find her anywhere"],[3150,3291,"and she left her phone in her room."],[3325,3491,"What do you mean you can't find her anywhere?"],[3512,3612,"I don't know, Dad."],[3770,3908,"I took care of her."],[4070,4170,"Where is she, Meredith?"],[4200,4370,"I sent her away to boarding school."],[4458,4642,"Chris, I think it's better"],[4642,4828,"you two have some time apart."],[4866,4950,"Boarding school?"],[5045,5241,"The school year hasn't even started yet."],[5341,5483,"And she left all of her clothes in her room"],[5483,5616,"as well as her phone, so you better start"],[5616,5741,"making some sense right now."]],"47":[[0,179,"Well, she must have left in a hurry."],[187,387,"I told her that the bus was waiting for her"],[387,508,"last night and..."],[508,562,"Last night?"],[758,933,"What school bus runs at night?"],[1237,1362,"You're lying to me, Meredith."],[1429,1550,"I swear I'm gonna find out"],[1550,1687,"what the fuck is going on here."],[1687,1775,"Do you understand me?"],[3087,3533,"My, my, my."],[3583,3716,"Look at you."],[3783,3937,"So scared."],[4045,4320,"Don't be scared, little angel."],[4491,4737,"You'll never know what you'll get into."],[5662,5879,"Doris, you work the night shift, don't you?"],[5887,6004,"Yes, Chris, I..."],[6004,6075,"Where's Jenny?"],[6329,6808,"Please don't say anything to anyone."]],"48":[[475,604,"You didn't like that?"],[725,808,"Too bad."],[895,1004,"There's more that came."],[2800,2875,"Are you okay?"],[2891,2966,"Did he hurt you?"],[2966,3175,"I'm fine. I wish you'd just get me out of here."],[3175,3329,"Okay, I'll get you home. It's okay."],[3329,3458,"Chris! Chris, watch out!"],[4187,4260,"Let's go."],[5129,5245,"Is she okay?"],[5479,5787,"God damn it! Why is she still alive?"]],"49":[[395,541,"Oh my god, honey!"],[591,700,"Where have you been?"],[775,882,"I'm worried sick."],[1033,1170,"Don't talk to me."],[1233,1425,"Are you even my real mother?"],[1483,1604,"Wait, what's going on?"],[1604,1704,"What's she talking about?"],[1704,1862,"Meredith here organized"],[1862,2029,"to kidnap her own daughter, isn't that right?"],[2162,2404,"I don't know what you're going on about, son."],[2466,2558,"I was here all night."],[2558,2741,"Save it for the cops."],[2758,2958,"They're here and they're not going anywhere."],[3283,3395,"You're under arrest."],[3395,3554,"You have the right to remain silent."],[3558,3737,"Anything you say will be used against you"],[3737,3816,"in a court of law."],[3916,4066,"There's been a mistake."],[4145,4337,"I've done nothing wrong."],[4375,4662,"All I wanted was stay married into the rich?"],[4733,4916,"Don't take me away."],[4933,5041,"No! Tim!"],[5104,5166,"Jenny!"],[5237,5366,"Mommy loves you."]],"50":[[8,229,"Come on, raise those hands guys!"],[370,470,"God damn it!"],[1441,1704,"We are going from 21 to nothing at this point!"],[2108,2158,"Chris!"],[2308,2387,"You're back!"],[2391,2620,"Holy shit, Chris is back!"],[2620,2804,"Just in time to save our asses!"],[2854,2973,"Get on that field, son."],[2973,3158,"We needed you like yesterday!"],[3812,3908,"Go Chris!"],[4400,4477,"Yeah!"],[4477,4550,"Let's go."],[4584,4708,"Let's go, baby!"],[5158,5220,"Yeah!"]],"51":[[183,337,"Chris, how do you feel about"],[337,479,"the championship game next week?"],[479,716,"You literally pulled this team back from the dead."],[750,958,"Well, I'm really confident that my team"],[958,1087,"and I are going to win the championship."],[1087,1216,"We're going to kill it no problem."],[1283,1528,"Chris, is it true that you were involved"],[1528,1683,"with your stepsister Jenny?"],[1683,1904,"Is that why you haven't been playing?"],[1958,2158,"Can we actually avoid that question?"],[2208,2333,"Chris, your girlfriend Natalie"],[2333,2554,"seems pretty determined to marry you."],[2587,2670,"Any regrets about going"],[2670,2831,"for your stepsister instead?"],[2841,3033,"My son is not dating his stepsister."],[3033,3216,"Meredith, an atrocious individual"],[3216,3346,"and a poor judgment on my part,"],[3346,3462,"has been arrested."],[3462,3595,"Here I have the divorce papers."],[3595,3725,"So she is no longer my wife,"],[3737,3854,"which means that Jenny"],[3854,4025,"is no longer Chris's stepsister."],[4387,4529,"Well, you heard that, everyone."],[4587,4875,"Jenny Taylor is officially my girlfriend."]],"52":[[70,270,"I didn't know you got the divorce finalized so quick."],[345,495,"Once you know it's a mistake,"],[495,662,"you gotta fix it fast."],[729,904,"I was wrong about you and Jenny, Chris."],[904,1050,"You two deserve each other."],[1129,1225,"Thanks, though."],[1329,1433,"Now focus on the game"],[1433,1558,"and treat your girl right, yeah?"],[2091,2145,"Hi."],[2508,2854,"So, did Mr. Riggins finally approve of us?"],[3008,3145,"Seems that way, Ms. Taylor."],[3191,3354,"You know, it's been a long,"],[3354,3529,"hard summer keeping you secret."],[3725,4025,"Be honest, Chris. When did you lay eyes on me?"],[4066,4237,"Right when you walked in the door."]]}